il.co.ilrd.hashtable

Class HashTable<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.co.ilrd.hashtable.HashTable<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of keys maintained by this map
    V - the type of mapped values
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Map<K,V>

    public class HashTable<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Map<K,V>
    A custom implementation of a hash table, which implements the Map interface. This class provides basic operations such as put, get, remove, and iteration over keys, values, and entries.
